OL,5, Indian women face discrimination in the
OL,6, job market and earn less than men even 
OL,7, when they have the same qualifications 
OL,8, and experience, a new report says.     
OL,10,FOxfam India's Discrimination Report    
OL,11,F2022 blames "societal and employers'   
OL,12,Fprejudices" for women's lower wages.   
OL,14,FOther marginalised communities also    
OL,15,Fsuffered discrimination in the job     
OL,16,Fmarket, the report found.              
OL,18,FThese included those at the bottom of  
OL,19,Fthe caste system, tribespeople and     
OL,20,Fmembers of the Muslim community.       
